`excel_test_file.xlsx` parseExcel wb!

@wb keys each. k!
    $"=== {@k} ===" wl
    @wb @k get? 1 enumerateN each.
        2unpack row!, rowNum!
        @row 1 enumerateN each.
            2unpack cell!, colNum!
            $"{@rowNum}:{@colNum}:{@cell type}|{@cell str}" wl
        end
    "---" wl
    end
end
